{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"英雄象","authors":["福庚"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":1,"day":10}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"福庚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线和英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快马不怕路远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝刀不怕使唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真金不怕火炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄不怕万难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起总路线金钥匙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开百宝山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抡起总路线宝刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把右倾思想劈个稀巴烂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨上总路线快马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天跃过二十年；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举总路线大旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红遍社会主义艳阳天!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一往直前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有洋天车咱们干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有好焊条咱们焊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有东西有好汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不讲价钱不要条件。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右倾姻云一扫光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥手拨开铜官山——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要的是多快好省，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲的是提前发电!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接任务"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘接任务，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜管立刻要焊住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提前一月完成定额，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全靠这一着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缺少铁面罩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙上花手帕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开电门“叭叭叭”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春电火迎风闪烁!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人说哪来的新娘子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她一声不响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干完擦擦汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸皮肤往下脱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劝她赶快抹点药，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她说:“管这干什么!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定要蛟龙早早吞吐电火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管叫江南日不落!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命班"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天闹高潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜搞发明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土坡上画图形，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手电当明灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这算哪一班?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么弄得清!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫它“革命班”也可以，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反正一股劲——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向机械设备要劳力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把荒山洪水变黄金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登天路上找捷径，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬腿跨过九重云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(1959年冬，写在新安江新高潮中)"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}